To find the original publication date, I'll need to look for more specific information. According to recent research, BERT was first introduced in the paper "BERT: Pre-training of Deep Bidirectional Transformers for Language Understanding" by Devlin et al. at the 2019 Conference of the North American Chapter of the Association for Computational Linguistics (NAACL).     

